Package: beastr
Type: Package
Title: Better Environmental/Animal Sensor/Telemetry Repository
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jon Weissman
Maintainer: Jon Weissman <jweissma@gmail.com>
Description: Manage wildlife telemetry data.
    This package provides the infrastructure needed to manage wildlife telemetry
    data. There are functions to read in raw data, build a database that 
    links sensor data to animals, filter bad data, do basic analyses, and export
    data for use in other applications.
License: AGPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
